Provider<MarkBounds>
public abstract class MarkBoundsProvider extends MarksBaseProvider<MarkBoundsProvider,MarkBounds>
An abstract provider for MarkBounds.

This class extends MarksBaseProvider and specializes it for providing MarkBounds objects. It serves as a base class for concrete implementations that provide specific mark bounds.
